Domain: World

Description: 
Handles the physical environments, grid systems, cell and planet-level map interactions.

Controllers:
- FactionController: Manages relationships, alliances, hostility, and faction-level data.
- GlobalMapController: Interacts with the planet map (WorldLayer), world tiles, and traveling caravans.
- MapController: Manages the local play area, weather, temperature, terrain grids, and cell data.